articles.title: Moldova narrowly votes to secure path toward EU membership after accusing Russia of interference - The Associated Press
articles.description: Electoral data shows that Moldovans have voted by a razor-thin majority in favor of securing the country’s path toward European Union membership. The pro-Western president is again accusing foreign interference and “criminal groups” of trying to undermine the…
